ERROR:ASSIGN_IN_IF: do not use assignment in if condition
#96: FILE: fs/configfs/file.c:137:
+		if ((retval = fill_read_buffer(file->f_path.dentry,buffer)))

Do not use assignments in if condition.
Example::

  if ((foo = bar(...)) < BAZ) {

should be written as::

  foo = bar(...);
  if (foo < BAZ) {

